data.description: Back on the market at no fault to the seller. Seller is offering VA assumable mortgage at a 2.75% rate!!! This gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2 bath brick home is a must see that is sure to meet your family's needs and hearts desires. Your new home is located in a established and desirable Lee Farms community. This beautiful home has a large living area that is perfect for entertaining friends and family around the holidays, a large master suite, fireplace,breakfast nook with bay windows overlooking the backyard, and a split floor plan design to name a few. Outside you will notice the large enclosed porch, large patio, and the fenced in lot that is perfect for the kids and pets to roam and play. The neighborhood also offers a community playground and easy commute to our local bases and beaches
